{"tid":357699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"渝男飲假酒中毒 以真酒解毒","createTime":"2017-08-13T06:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T07:11:13.000Z","uid":13468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34345445766aa68bd52e00beaa3fd0fc86c94802","tid":357699,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"渝男飲假酒中毒 以真酒解毒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以毒攻毒只是小說情節？少年你太年輕了！重慶石柱市一名52歲男子，誤買假酒喝下大量甲醇，導致急性中毒。醫生竟叫他喝下60度的白酒，以真酒解假酒。<br />\n<br />\n事主傳先生在醫生的指導下，每小時喝下35毫升的白酒。醫生指出，甲醇中毒一般最常見的原因，主要為誤服假酒，或是服用工業用酒精而引起的中毒。甲醇本身是無毒的，但甲醇經人體代謝會產生甲醛和甲酸，對人體產生傷害。<br />\n<br />\n當真酒喝下去後，酒裡的乙醇就會和血液中的甲醇產生競爭，甲醇不會再在代謝中產生作用，達到解毒。<br />\n<br />\n傳先生坦言，自己以8元買到一枝酒，當時還以為買到好貨，未料喝了整枝卻頭昏無力，出現劇烈嘔吐的情況。未料，原來該酒是假酒，經過今次教訓傳先生不敢再買平酒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/980039/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F980039%2F&d=IxxQi8CEL8ygLsLPGP1XSZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b53ab3cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F980039%2F&h=29a29419\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/980039/</a>"},{"pid":"1d855215f5e108af3ee9e436bb3b73941c198b20","tid":357699,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"8蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c554cda7e408e9169403fcfc5b5d8e52380f949","tid":357699,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順手驗下個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88486446e4db4bbf98f7725e66daddbb6747562","tid":357699,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"上周五（4日）凌晨，傅男再被轉院至重慶醫科大學附屬第二醫院急救。當時他已陷入昏迷，醫生搶救時竟作出不可思議的決定，叫其家人上街買酒，「說要買五六十度的高度酒，用來解毒！」 <br />\n<br />\n原來醫生是要以「真酒」解「假酒」的毒。醫生解釋，因為傅男中毒情況嚴重，採用透析治療清除血液中的甲醇時，會帶走乙醇（真酒）中的解毒成分，因此做透析時，每小時會讓傅男喝35毫升白酒，自上周五以來，傅男已喝了近1公斤白酒；傅男血液中的甲醇含量亦由每公升487毫克，降至每公升4.6毫克，終於康復出院。"},{"pid":"95ba955c617f092bda68f8d29e0fe92888abd120","tid":357699,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfd8c6b7eb4482047d4ee1bf0525e7d50a59c2f","tid":357699,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"人地一般做法係直接吊鹽水咁打Ethanol solution入去<br />\n佢就叫人買酒飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果今次買都買到假就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf8767887e726884a7f576794661b2700dbefa7","tid":357699,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>8蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順手驗下個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}